(369, 3, '2007-08-11 22:45:43', '2013-04-11 22:43:06', '51 Irish Coffees. The speed and precision the bartenders employed to get this order done was astonishing... I''m just glad one of those belonged to me. \n\nAs it turns out, I was alerted to another photo randomly taken by someone I don''t know at the same time, from a different angle. You can see my left hand and camera in this shot.... \n<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/bsii/1097620023/">www.flickr.com/photos/bsii/1097620023/</a>\n\nAll Rights Reserved 2013<a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/2.0/" title="Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs License">Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs License</a>', 'Irish Coffee at the Buena Vista', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'irish-coffee-at-the-buena-vista', '', '', '2007-08-11 22:45:43', '2013-04-11 22:43:06', '', 219, '', 1, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
