(222, 1, '2011-04-16 00:00:54', '2011-04-16 00:00:54', '<a href="http://www.hasselbladusa.com/media/1500490/india-10214_web.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://www.hasselbladusa.com/media/1500490/india-10214_web.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="360" /></a>Yesterday, the <a href="http://www.ulearn.ie/english_school_dublin" target="_blank">English School Dublin</a> organized a visit to the actual exhibition of the Gallery of photography: <a href="http://www.galleryofphotography.ie/exhibitions/Steve_McCurry.html" target="_blank">Steve McCurry | Worlds of color</a>, as always, after the <a href="http://www.ulearn.ie/quality_english_courses_dublin" target="_blank">English Class</a> of the morning. I didn’t go because I went there two times before but I’m going to talk a little bit about <a href="http://www.stevemccurry.com/main.php" target="_blank">Steve Mc Curry</a> and this exhibition.\r\n\r\nSteve Mc Curry is an American photojournalist. He was born in Philadelphia in 1950. His<a href="http://mannaismayaadventure.files.wordpress.com/2010/07/300px-sharbat_gula-afghan-girl.jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://mannaismayaadventure.files.wordpress.com/2010/07/300px-sharbat_gula-afghan-girl.jpg" alt="" width="284" height="448" /></a> most recognized photo is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afghan_Girl" target="_blank">Afghan Girl</a>. This girl was photographed when she was living as a refugee in Pakistan, during the time of the Soviet Occupation. She was around 12 years then and 17 years before, his team located the girl in a remote region of Afghanistan, she had returned to her native country from the refugee camp in 1992. There are both photographies in the exhibition, including some more, taken by McCurry, amazingly beautiful.\r\n\r\nThis exhibition finishes at 24th of this month, and the gallery is open from Tuesdays to Saturdays between 11am and 6pm, and on Sundays between 1 and 6pm and it''s free.', 'Steve McCurry exhibition in Gallery of Photography Dublin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'steve-mccurry-exhibition-in-gallery-of-photography-dublin', '', '', '2013-04-11 15:59:51', '2013-04-11 15:59:51', '', 0, 'http://dev.wp/?p=222', 0, 'post', '', 0),
