 the chance to watch a match, but I would like to watch one. And it’s normal to see children with hurleys on the streets.</p>', 'HURLING AND GAELIC FOOTBALL', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '288-revision-3', '', '', '2011-05-07 19:01:34', '2011-05-07 19:01:34', '', 288, 'http://dev.wp/?p=291', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
