(738, 3, '2013-04-12 06:19:55', '2013-04-12 05:19:55', '<iframe src="https://embed.spotify.com/?uri=spotify:track:7yAji4t1cAxthnsE3WcsIc" height="100" width="550" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 0.9rem;">And here are some words that all mean "song"</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong style="font-size: 0.9rem; font-style: italic;">Tune</strong><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; font-style: italic;"> - Your Dad can use this </span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=" font-size: 0.9rem;"><strong>Track</strong> - DJ''s and people who want to be cool use this</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=" font-size: 0.9rem;"><strong>DItty</strong> - Your Grandfather could use this</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(Oh, and "<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>abducted</strong></span>" means to be <em>taken away </em>without your permission. Think Liam Neeson''s daughter in the movie Taken. ''She was <em>abducted</em> by criminals.'')', 'Abducted by The Cults', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '423-revision-60', '', '', '2013-04-12 06:19:55', '2013-04-12 05:19:55', '', 423, 'http://dev.wp/423-revision-60/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
